eu.kerdev.testApp.service

Class ContractImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.kerdev.testApp.service.ContractImporter

  • @Component
public class ContractImporter
extends java.lang.Object
    Object imports data from xlsx file. Expected headers for columns are defined in ContractColumnHeader enum. Import process doesn't require the columns to be in order
